sequenceDiagram
  participant Edge as Edge App
  participant API as Express API
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant WS as Socket.IO
  participant UI as React UI

  Edge->>API: POST /sync/deliveries
  API->>DB: BEGIN
  API->>DB: INSERT ... ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
  DB-->>API: ok
  API->>DB: COMMIT
  API->>WS: emit coffee_synced
  WS-->>UI: coffee_synced
  UI->>API: GET /metrics + dashboards
  API->>DB: SELECT aggregates
  DB-->>API: data
  API-->>UI: dashboard payload
